emuInput.TitMainTitle: Portrait of groom Charles A. Mitchell Jr. and bride Maryann Harris Mitchell, standing behind five tiered wedding cake, in interior with dark curtain in background
emuInput.CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, March 11, 1961, pg. 16 reads: "Smiling Happily, following their recent wedding, are Mr. and Mrs. Charles A. Mitchell Jr. The couple was married in rectory of Holy Rosary Church.  The bride is the former Maryan Harris, Daughter of Mr. and Mrs. Robert Harris Sr. of Upland St. - Harris Photo."
